<div class="hero">
    <div class="hero__section hero__section--left">
        <div class="hero__content hero__content--left">
            <div class="hero__content-top">
                <img class="hero__content-decoration" src="/assets/images/image_1.svg" alt="Header Accent">
                <h2 class="hero__content-header">
                    WordPress Geniuses
                    <span>
                        <img src="/assets/images/image_4.svg" />
                        At Your Service
                    </span>
                </h2>
            </div>

            <p class="hero__content-p">While WordPress makes it easy for anyone
                to build a website without knowing how to code, there's always a
                chance of running into an issue that you don't know how to fix.
                That's where we come in! DreamHost's friendly, pro-level
                customer support representatives are the best
                in the biz, skillfully striving to always make sure your
                hosting needs are met.
            </p>
            <p class="hero__content-p">Having an issue? Just let us know - when it comes to WordPress
                hosting, no question is ever too simple or too complex.
            </p>
            <div class="hero__content-link--wrapper">
                <a class="hero__content-link" href="/">Learn More &rarr;</a>
            </div>
        </div>
    </div>
    <div class="hero__section hero__section--right">
        <div class="hero__content hero__content--right">
            <img class="hero__content-image" src="./assets/images/image_2.png" alt="WordPress Hosting Geniuses">
        </div>
    </div>
</div>

<style lang="scss">
    .hero {
        display: flex;
        flex-direction: row;
        align-items: center;
        justify-content: center;
        margin-top: clamp(2rem, 3vw, 4rem);

        &__section {
            width: 100%;

            &--left {
                flex: 1;
                display: flex;
                padding-left: 7.8vw;
            }

            &--right {
                width: 100%;
                flex-basis: 45%;
                padding-right: 3vw;
            }
        }

        &__content {
            display: flex;
            flex-direction: column;
            justify-content: center;
            width: 100%;

            &--right {
                align-items: center;
            }

            &-top {
                position: relative;
            }

            &-decoration {
                position: absolute;
                left: -217px;
                bottom: 26px;

                @media screen and (max-width: 1368px) {
                    bottom: 26px;
                }
            }

            &-header {
                font-size: clamp(42px, 2.6vw, 64px);
                font-weight: bold;
                line-height: clamp(60px, 3vw, 80px);
                margin-bottom: 1rem;

                span {
                    display: block;

                    img {
                        width: 2vw;
                        height: 2vw;
                    }
                }

            }

            &-image {
                width: clamp(500px, 100%, 800px);
                max-width: 100%;
                height: auto;
            }

            &-p {
                font-size: clamp(16px, 1.6vw, 24px);
                line-height: 40px;
                margin-bottom: 1rem;
                font-weight: 500;
            }

            &-link {
                font-size: 1.5rem;
                font-weight: 600;
                line-height: 1.5;
                margin-bottom: 1rem;

                &--wrapper {
                    display: flex;
                    justify-content: flex-start;
                    margin-bottom: 1rem;
                }
            }

        }
    }
